episodes.title: My Response To Krishna Sahay's "I Snuck Into A Real Life Cult" Video
episodes.description:
I applaud Krishna Sahay a fellow East Indian of my racial community for calling out the Iglesia Ni Cristo Filipino cult organization in his original video that I am responding to.
